				<td>
					<B>A BRIEF HISTORY</B>
					<br>
					R&J Metal Fabricators was started by 
					Reg Jones in 1959 as a "One Man" shop. Since then, we have grown to have 40 
					full time employees and 24,000 square feet of fabrication area.
					<br>
					<br>
